chat.Mark Description:
The current marking feature is in beta.

After clicking to add a mark, you need to select a knowledge base to store the marked data. You can use this feature to quickly mark questions and expected answers to guide the model's response next time.

Currently, like other data in the knowledge base, the marking feature is influenced by the model and does not guarantee 100% accuracy after marking.

Marked data only syncs one-way with the knowledge base. If the knowledge base modifies the marked data, the log display of marked data cannot be synchronized.
